OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FThere's been much anticipation for the
OL,8,Flatest instalment of Peaky Blinders,
OL,9,Fthis time hitting the big screens.
OL,11,FAlongside Cillian Murphy and the rest
OL,12,Fof the star-studded cast, Cumbria has
OL,13,Fplayed a key part in The Immortal Man.
OL,15,FIn 2024, Netflix took over Calder
OL,16,FAbbey to film key scenes of the movie,
OL,17,Fwhich was released on Friday, 6th of
OL,18,FMarch.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
