OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FThe team behind the building now hopes
OL,8,Fthe appeal of the hit show will put
OL,9,FCalder Bridge on the map.
OL,11,FBuster Evans first started as a
OL,12,Fgardener here four years ago and has
OL,13,Fsince become site manager.
OL,15,FHe's since fallen in love with the
OL,16,Fbuilding and wants to bring it back to
OL,17,Flife.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FHe spent the best part of a year
OL,8,Ftalking to location scouts before any
OL,9,Ffilming began. "It was amazing to be
OL,10,Fpart of it," he said.
OL,12,F"The filming transformed the site; we
OL,13,Fhad about 200 people on site. We're
OL,14,Fhoping for some really good attention
OL,15,Fcoming back from that. Hopefully, it
OL,16,Fdraws enough attention where we can
OL,17,Factually do more."
OL,19,FThose who've already seen the
OL,20,Fblockbuster say the location plays a
OL,21,Fkey part in the film.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
