PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FCrews spent three long days filming
OL,8,Faround the derelict 12th-century
OL,9,Fabbey, and also shooting within the
OL,10,Fattached Georgian manor house.
OL,12,FMonks founded Calder Abbey in the 12th
OL,13,Fcentury, but the reign of Henry VIII
OL,14,Fleft it in ruins.
OL,16,FWhile the Georgian manor house was
OL,17,Fadded later, the building was
OL,18,Fconverted into flats in the sixties.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
