PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FBut that building has been left empty
OL,8,F- apart from a caretaker who lives on-
OL,9,Fsite - so it is in a state of
OL,10,Fdisrepair.
OL,12,F"It's difficult to restore these
OL,13,Fproperties because it is a Grade I
OL,14,Flisted property," Buster explains,
OL,15,Fnoting that makes it more expensive.
OL,17,F"It's going to take a community effort
OL,18,Fto try and help restore this building
OL,19,Fand this site. If we can do that, or
OL,20,Feven come close, if we can preserve
OL,21,Fit, that's all that matters."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FIn recent years tours have restarted,
OL,8,Fand location fees were paid by
OL,9,FNetflix, but they don't cover the
OL,10,Festimated millions needed to restore
OL,11,Fthe building.
OL,13,F"Realistically, we're looking for
OL,14,Ffunding ourselves to try and help
OL,15,Frestore it. Our end goal is to
OL,16,Fpreserve this site and open it up for
OL,17,Fthe public."
OL,19,FA team of volunteers has been
OL,20,Fpreserving the building as best they
OL,21,Fcan.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
