PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,FMichael Harrison moved to Calder
OL,8,FBridge two and a half years ago and
OL,9,Finstantly fell in love with the site
OL,10,Fwhile on a walk in the area.
OL,12,FHe's since spent his spare time
OL,13,Fgardening and performing minor repairs
OL,14,Fto the building.
OL,16,FHe says the work gives him immense
OL,17,Fsatisfaction: "I feel very fortunate.
OL,18,FI feel almost as though I'm part of
OL,19,Fthe house, part of the history. It's
OL,20,Fjust giving something back.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
