FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1773076274
OL,3,CThe volunteers battling to save
OL,4,CCumbrian abbey used in new Peaky
OL,5,CBlinders film
OL,7,F"There's a massive amount to do. When
OL,8,Fyou look at the house itself, it's
OL,9,Fdeteriorating quite rapidly, so it's
OL,10,Fjust nice to see things start to
OL,11,Fimprove."
OL,13,FHe also happens to be a Peaky Blinders
OL,14,Ffan: "The fact that they filmed a part
OL,15,Fof the film here is amazing for the
OL,16,Farea. It's just going to put it on the
OL,17,Fmap."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/8
